{
  "stem": "19596.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 355.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I was introduced that I could carry them in the risk of my life, naturally.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In My life, not my-- to carry them into the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They would organize all this, the butcher.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were non-Jewish, all non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I spoke good languages and I was, you know, known to be reliable and a survivor and all that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Through connections I got that job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "SS.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To SS staff, to the commanders and all that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Man, it's not a job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They made me a proposition if I want to do it, to come, because they had a way of me doing it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I said, what the way?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, we put you in that, what you call Scheisskommando?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What's Scheisskomando?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] the shit kommando.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That is emptying-- emptying the-- the latrines.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that you-- I would be hung.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not for the SS, to bring it in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Stolen goods.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Steal it from there and bring it into the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would be hung.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So, you know, I said to myself, what have I got to lose?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My life, or this, or this, or this?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because I was desperate for something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyhow, I joined the what you call Scheisskommando.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's a kommando were you get big gloves, big overalls, rubber boots, and you empty the latrines with a big stick.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You empty it, the outside latrines, on working places.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you have to empty it into a container, which is a huge container drawn by four horses on a cart.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So me and another two guys went out with two guards.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whereever we went out, we always had two armed guards with us, you know, with the rifles.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
